  <brief_title>Study of REGN668/SAR231893 in Adult Patients With Extrinsic Moderate-to-Severe Atopic Dermatitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Repeat-Dose Study of the Efficacy, Safety, Tolerability, and Pharmacodynamics of Subcutaneously-Administered REGN668 in Adult Patients With Extrinsic Moderate-to-Severe Atopic Dermatitis</official_title>
