  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To assess the clinical efficacy of repeated subcutaneous (SC) doses of REGN668/SAR231893 in
      adult patients with moderate-to-severe atopic dermatitis (AD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
